<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.ClearDeviceFilters" Title="ClearDeviceFilters method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator">IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    ClearDeviceFilters
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ClearDeviceFilters</TypeRef> method removes all filters which have been applied to the filtered
      device set returned by <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.GetFilteredDevices">GetFilteredDevices</PageRef>.
      After calling this method, the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.GetFilteredDevices">GetFilteredDevices</PageRef>
      method will return the same set of devices as <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.GetAllDevices">GetAllDevices</PageRef>
      until more filters are applied by calling one of the device filtering methods such as <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.FilterDevicesOfType">FilterDevicesOfType</PageRef>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void ClearDeviceFilters();]]></Code>
  </Section>
